title: Farm Weighting Adjustments
body:
We're proposing an update to the #PancakeSwap farm rewards:

🥞  Reduce rewards to low liquidity / low volume farms
🥞  Reduce rewards to farms with excessive liquidity
🥞  Decrease dilution of rewards to key farms
🥞  Make room for more new Syrup Pools!
